WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.893
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.893 --> 00:00:03.063
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.063 --> 00:00:05.120
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:20.960
Well, we got an article somebody sent us talking about Iran threatening our military if Trump strikes Iran, that there would be retaliations against our bases overseas.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:40.331
So, I was like, "This is exactly what the Lord showed me in prayer to y'all when we were praying to pray for Iraq and the military base in Iraq, that I saw drones flying in and dropping stuff out of them and hurting our troops.

00:00:40.331 --> 00:00:45.839
" That we would pray for a supernatural hedge of protection around our troops.

00:00:45.839 --> 00:00:54.160
So whenever Iran immediately threatened our military bases, I thought, "Wow, this is what the Lord was showing us.

00:00:54.160 --> 00:01:01.566
" And so we're going to keep continual prayer over our military men and women that are serving our country.

00:01:01.566 --> 00:01:10.680
Then the Lord was showing me Trump was trying to devise a plan to strike Iran and that it would be through Israel.

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:14.251
And so he had three different plan options.

00:01:14.251 --> 00:01:24.331
And it was like I said in the spirit when I was looking in the spirit, it was like chess trying to think ahead strategically.

00:01:24.331 --> 00:01:27.093
"If we do this what will they do?

00:01:27.093 --> 00:01:29.192
If we do this what will they do?

00:01:29.192 --> 00:01:30.584
And how will we do this?

00:01:30.584 --> 00:01:42.000
" And so the Lord showed me when I was praying last night, I was praying over strategic battle plans that Trump would have the wisdom to know what to do.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:44.720
Praying over him to have the wisdom to know what to do.

00:01:44.720 --> 00:01:53.697
Praying over him to have foresight to see way in the future of knowing this is what's going to be the retaliation of this, you know.

00:01:53.697 --> 00:01:58.514
And right now I know being diplomatic is what he's doing.

00:01:59.439 --> 00:02:02.239
"Hey, you all stop this or we're going to do this.

00:02:02.239 --> 00:02:08.040
" So, he's not going to go right in and just guns blazing without having some diplomacy is what I'm trying to say.

00:02:08.040 --> 00:02:09.827
There has to be some kind of diplomacy.

00:02:09.827 --> 00:02:17.462
So, right now we're seeing diplomacy because he has to justify what he's going to do to all the other nations of the world.

00:02:17.462 --> 00:02:22.740
"Hey, we're going to stop Iran from having a nuclear weapon in the Middle East.

00:02:23.420 --> 00:02:35.519
" A nuclear Iran is a bad Iran, and really, bottom line, I believe they probably already have one, but you have to go about it this way because it's more tactful.

00:02:35.519 --> 00:02:37.340
So, that's what we're seeing right now.

00:02:37.340 --> 00:02:38.639
We're seeing it in the news.

00:02:38.639 --> 00:02:46.699
Everything the Lord showed us clear back before he was inaugurated, we're seeing it in the news today.

00:02:46.699 --> 00:02:55.580
So we see Trump saying things on Truth Social, and so he is saying that on the second they're going to implement these tariffs.

00:02:55.580 --> 00:02:58.1000
So we need to pray over the economy.

00:02:58.1000 --> 00:03:04.820
I know what the Lord showed me about a major economic crash.

00:03:04.820 --> 00:03:08.052
I know what he told me about this.

00:03:08.052 --> 00:03:10.629
I've told you this this time last year.

00:03:10.629 --> 00:03:13.635
I've told you this for a while now.

00:03:13.635 --> 00:03:26.229
But I know what the Lord showed me about October in the intercessory prayer that we did as a nation, praying and asking God to delay what was coming.

00:03:26.229 --> 00:03:28.771
I don't believe it stopped.

00:03:28.771 --> 00:03:30.514
I believe we delayed it.

00:03:30.514 --> 00:03:37.613
And that's what I'm praying about: keeping the line strong, having a rectangular window of opportunity.

00:03:37.613 --> 00:03:46.040
It looked like a rectangle whenever I was looking over in it, to believe for the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:49.485
I told you there's hard days coming.

00:03:49.485 --> 00:03:58.043
I told you there's a great shaking to awaken, and I believe we're seeing the birthing pains of that right now.

00:03:58.043 --> 00:04:01.840
We see all the things of him trying to make America great.

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:05.200
Folks, it was a mess.

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:13.726
This was a catastrophic mess of what the Biden and Harris administration had and where we were going.

00:04:13.726 --> 00:04:19.626
If she would have won, I'm telling you, we would be in a totally different ballgame right now.

00:04:19.626 --> 00:04:26.698
But I believe with God's grace, we're having a window of opportunity to fix some things.

00:04:26.698 --> 00:04:30.187
Now, is it too far gone to fix?

00:04:30.653 --> 00:04:32.053
Only God knows.

00:04:32.053 --> 00:04:34.693
But we see the things happening.

00:04:34.693 --> 00:04:37.000
But I'm believing for a window.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:51.947
I'm believing for a window for the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous, for the remnant to have enough finances to take and be able to do the gospel in a major way for what I've seen coming.

00:04:51.947 --> 00:04:53.160
I'm talking disasters.

00:04:53.160 --> 00:05:00.091
I'm praying over another EMP attack that I've seen that I've not talked about a lot because people get all freaked out about it.

00:05:00.091 --> 00:05:04.000
But I'm telling you, I've seen some dark things.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:08.983
And the Lord has told me, "Brandon, there is a humbling coming to America.

00:05:08.983 --> 00:05:11.897
There's a great shaking coming to America.

00:05:12.530 --> 00:05:16.400
" I told you about the heart and the black of the heart upon the land.

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:18.987
And there was a little sliver, and I believe that's the remnant.

00:05:18.987 --> 00:05:33.040
I believe that's the people like you and me praying and interceding for this nation, and that there was a sliver of red and all this other when the hearts were collected combined, it was all black.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:36.479
And the further it went out, the darker it got.

00:05:36.819 --> 00:05:38.519
And this is another thing.

00:05:38.519 --> 00:05:47.680
After the word the Lord gave us last night when we were praying, he showed me a major cleaning of the house again.

00:05:47.960 --> 00:05:52.479
And I'm telling y'all, I could feel the Lord's—it wasn't anger.

00:05:52.479 --> 00:06:03.359
It was correction for sure of the churches not taking their authority, preaching the gospel like they should.

00:06:03.359 --> 00:06:10.800
And he said, "Brandon, you're being too kind, basically saying that the church is lukewarm in these areas.

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:12.840
" He said, "It's not lukewarm.

00:06:12.840 --> 00:06:13.773
They're cold.

00:06:13.773 --> 00:06:17.406
" And they're feeding the people a cold, stale bread.

00:06:17.406 --> 00:06:21.840
Basically, the bread of affliction, just keeping them alive.

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:28.769
You know, it's like the prisoners when you don't want to feed them too much, you don't want them to die, but you just keep them alive.

00:06:28.769 --> 00:06:35.900
You know, whenever in bad war times, you don't want to give them enough strength to fight you, but they are there just to sustain life.

00:06:38.434 --> 00:06:42.992
And that's what's happening with a lot of churches from what I saw in the spirit.

00:06:42.992 --> 00:06:47.689
And he even brought it up from Maine all the way down to Pennsylvania and all that.

00:06:47.689 --> 00:06:54.960
I saw it in the vision and the Lord showed me, he said, "These people are from every denomination, tribe, and tongue.

00:06:55.486 --> 00:07:01.360
They are not teaching the people how to stand and live by faith.

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:03.863
" And I'm thankful a lot of you all are here.

00:07:03.863 --> 00:07:06.679
I hope this channel has brought you hope.

00:07:06.679 --> 00:07:12.080
I pray that we're giving you that meat that you're getting fed here.

00:07:12.500 --> 00:07:21.269
I thought when I went to Florida and we were driving through all those areas, I thought there has to be an oasis somewhere.

00:07:21.269 --> 00:07:32.525
There has to be that oasis that people can go and drink from the well, drink and get filled up by the Holy Ghost every single day.

00:07:32.525 --> 00:07:43.022
And I know you can do that on your own personal times, but I hope that you can get that here, that Diana and I, we and the kids, we're praying for you.

00:07:43.022 --> 00:07:45.703
We believe that God is still on the throne.

00:07:45.703 --> 00:07:51.199
And it's like Billy Burke said, "Brandon, you've always got to bring hope.

00:07:51.199 --> 00:07:53.119
Hope to the people.

00:07:53.119 --> 00:07:56.663
Yeah, you deliver the hard words, but always bring hope.

00:07:56.994 --> 00:07:58.639
Tell the people there's hope.

00:07:58.639 --> 00:08:00.240
" And I believe there's hope.

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:05.386
Just like what he was telling me, and I believe that, and God bless him, I love Billy Burke.

00:08:05.386 --> 00:08:08.240
He is a friend and I am thankful for him.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:09.759
But I'm telling you all, there is hope there.

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:12.015
It's not all doom and gloom.

00:08:12.015 --> 00:08:15.429
It is not a time of just going "the sky's falling," Chicken Little.

00:08:15.429 --> 00:08:20.400
This is a time of rejoicing because our redemption is drawing nigh.

00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:26.949
And I believe with all my heart, we're about to see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

00:08:26.949 --> 00:08:33.549
And all the darkness and all the things that I'm telling you that if you stay horizontal, it can affect you.

00:08:33.549 --> 00:08:35.440
But if we keep vertical, it won't.

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:36.880
And I'm telling you, I'm believing God.

00:08:36.880 --> 00:08:38.594
I'm believing God for big.

00:08:38.594 --> 00:08:59.399
I'm believing God for a big 2025 in this cleaning of the house, of the exposing of the wickedness and doing the things that I've seen happening with the church preparing itself for this great, great move of God, birthing us out of prayer and getting ready for this major revival that's about to take place.

00:08:59.399 --> 00:09:03.790
I still believe for the supernatural wealth transfer to take place.

00:09:03.790 --> 00:09:05.940
I'm not letting that go.

00:09:05.940 --> 00:09:07.102
We need it.

00:09:07.102 --> 00:09:08.311
My family needs it.

00:09:08.311 --> 00:09:12.810
We need it for what God has told us to do, for what I know is coming.

00:09:12.810 --> 00:09:15.360
It's going to take major finances to do it.

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:17.786
And so we're just stretching out there.

00:09:17.786 --> 00:09:22.674
It's like the Lord said, 'Stretch forth your net to Peter,' whenever he was there.

00:09:22.674 --> 00:09:25.189
And he said, 'Lord, I've been fishing all night.

00:09:26.990 --> 00:09:27.680
I'm exhausted.

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:28.880
I'm ready to go home.

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:30.320
' That is basically what he was saying.

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:41.440
But Jesus said, 'Just trust me,' and he threw the net over on the side one more time and he got the biggest bumper crop he could ever hope or imagine or think.

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:45.901
And he's the 'exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think' God.

00:09:45.901 --> 00:09:48.672
And we believe—that's the way that Diana and I believe.

00:09:48.672 --> 00:09:52.285
We're believing for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:09:52.285 --> 00:09:54.513
I'm talking for major things.

00:09:54.513 --> 00:10:03.920
I don't get into it all on this YouTube channel to tell you what we're believing for because I don't want doubt and unbelief trying to hinder what I'm believing for.

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:06.400
I have to keep my eyes vertical.

00:10:06.400 --> 00:10:10.560
And if I tell people what I'm believing for, they're going to go, 'What?

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:11.588
' and it's a chokehold for me.

00:10:11.588 --> 00:10:15.314
So I don't need everybody speaking their doubt into what I'm believing for.

00:10:16.823 --> 00:10:25.919
I just keep things to myself and we keep things as a family, and we're just believing for big because I know what God has told us to do.

00:10:26.159 --> 00:10:32.800
It's going to be an international ministry and someway, somehow, I know that the Lord is calling us to do something huge.

00:10:33.050 --> 00:10:38.739
And even like the lady—I don't know who you were, but you sent Diana a really nice black purse last night.

00:10:39.419 --> 00:10:48.489
I polished that black purse up, and she got a pair of nice sandals that needed cleaning up; a lady just gave them to my wife.

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:53.040
So I was just taking the Magic Eraser and cleaning things up.

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:57.680
It's a blessing when people send you stuff and they try to be nice to you.

00:10:57.952 --> 00:11:03.240
I told Diana, 'We don't know who it is, but boy, your people just try to love on you.

00:11:03.240 --> 00:11:10.190
' They gave her a black purse, a coat, and stuff, and put it in a box to bless my wife last night.

00:11:10.190 --> 00:11:12.285
She was so excited to get those sandals.

00:11:12.285 --> 00:11:16.462
I said, 'Baby, let me clean them up for you and get that leather cleaned up and make it look nice.

00:11:16.462 --> 00:11:21.940
' We're just so grateful for people doing things like that for us.

00:11:21.940 --> 00:11:28.308
You don't have to, but whenever somebody just does something out of the kindness of their heart, you just want to say thank you.

00:11:28.308 --> 00:11:30.079
And Diana was just thankful.

00:11:30.079 --> 00:11:34.274
She sat there and said, 'You know, Brandon, I was praying for some sandals for the summer.

00:11:34.274 --> 00:11:35.268
' Isn't that amazing?

00:11:36.080 --> 00:11:40.320
And what was even more amazing, folks, is they were her size.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:46.747
Nobody knows what size of shoe my wife wears, but God put it on this lady's heart to send her shoes.

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:49.330
I thought, 'What a kindness!

00:11:49.330 --> 00:11:53.271
' So things like that blessed us.

00:11:53.608 --> 00:12:00.020
I took those shoes and I polished and cleaned them all up for her last night and got them all ready.

00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:01.200
She said, 'Thanks, baby.

00:12:01.200 --> 00:12:03.404
' It's just a blessing.

00:12:03.653 --> 00:12:10.571
I got the purse all cleaned up, put that leather cleaner on there, and polished that leather up until it smelled like brand new leather.

00:12:10.846 --> 00:12:12.080
I thought, 'What a blessing.

00:12:12.080 --> 00:12:14.389
' So we're just grateful.

00:12:14.389 --> 00:12:21.620
But I just wanted to tell whoever that was—you've never emailed before and there was no way to contact you to tell you thank you.

00:12:21.620 --> 00:12:27.465
So God bless you and know that we pray for you to have a great harvest.

00:12:28.085 --> 00:12:32.480
Diana said, 'Let's pray for her to have some leather purses back there.

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:34.080
' Blessings in everything.

00:12:38.050 --> 00:12:49.133
Like I said, you all, we are in Central Oklahoma, and all the areas of Oklahoma, Kansas, Texas, and Missouri get major tornadoes.

00:12:49.600 --> 00:12:55.228
I've told you I've seen major tornadoes, but you have authority over tornadoes.

00:12:55.936 --> 00:13:07.120
You as believers need to pray, not being afraid of tornado season in America or wherever you're at.

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:12.674
You have authority to pray and take authority over the storms.

00:13:12.674 --> 00:13:25.782
When the weatherman comes on and says, 'Hey, there's going to be golf-ball-sized hail, there's going to be baseball-sized hail, and it's going to come with 50-mile-per-hour winds that will break out windows and everything,' start praying in the spirit.

00:13:25.782 --> 00:13:32.400
Take authority over the storms, telling them, 'No, you will not do this over our house.

00:13:32.400 --> 00:13:36.022
You will not have destruction over our house.

00:13:36.022 --> 00:13:47.180
We bind this demonic storm and we tell you to cease and desist in your maneuvering,' just like Jesus did when he said, 'Peace, be still' to the storm.

00:13:47.180 --> 00:13:54.383
We are created in the image of God and we are joint heirs of Jesus Christ; and as he is, so are we in this world.

00:13:54.383 --> 00:14:00.308
Say that: 'As he is, so are we in this world.

00:14:00.308 --> 00:14:05.120
' And we take authority over that storm in the name of Jesus.

00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:08.983
We tell you to have peace, be still.

00:14:08.983 --> 00:14:11.919
And you'll see that storm as we're praying.

00:14:11.919 --> 00:14:15.690
You can see that storm part and it starts to fall apart.

00:14:15.690 --> 00:14:18.440
And all of a sudden, they'll have a tornado, 'Well, we just lost it.

00:14:18.440 --> 00:14:19.271
' And it's so funny.

00:14:19.271 --> 00:14:27.889
We laugh about it because we see the weatherman doing his best to try to tell us what's going on, but we're over there praying and binding and telling the storm to die.

00:14:28.580 --> 00:14:33.903
You can see it on the radar on the TV; that thing just falls apart.

00:14:33.903 --> 00:14:40.880
I believe every believer has that authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt you.

00:14:40.880 --> 00:14:52.171
I believe with all my heart that we have authority over the storms—not just spiritual storms, but physical storms, mental storms, whatever storm is trying to come against you.

00:14:52.171 --> 00:14:54.343
You have authority over the storm.

00:14:54.709 --> 00:14:57.269
I believe you should use your authority.

00:14:57.269 --> 00:14:59.013
Don't shy away from it.

00:14:59.013 --> 00:14:59.351
Call it.

00:15:00.027 --> 00:15:00.364
Speak to it.

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:01.320
Say, 'No.

00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:03.279
' And then pray for the rain.

00:15:11.348 --> 00:15:12.720
Say, 'Thank you, Father, for rain.

00:15:12.720 --> 00:15:13.839
Rain's a blessing.

00:15:13.839 --> 00:15:18.936
' You know, we have authority to call in the rain.

00:15:25.154 --> 00:15:25.531
Call in the low-pressure system.

00:15:29.600 --> 00:15:29.863
Say, 'Bring in the rain from the Gulf of America now.

00:15:29.863 --> 00:15:37.860
' Whatever we're going to call it, the Gulf of America, 'Bring forth the rain in Jesus' name.

00:15:37.860 --> 00:15:46.720
' And Father, we thank you, Lord, for the supernatural rain so that we don't have drought.

00:16:00.268 --> 00:16:00.596
We call forth rain—two or three inches of rain—and we say in the name of Jesus, drought's broken.

00:16:03.164 --> 00:16:04.071
We will not have this.

00:16:07.590 --> 00:16:07.920
You have to speak to your weather.

00:16:13.880 --> 00:16:14.130
We have dominion and authority just like Adam.

00:16:14.130 --> 00:16:20.419
Adam spoke and God gave Adam dominion over all the birds and all the fish and over all the animals.

00:16:20.419 --> 00:16:25.279
He gave us dominion over the earth, over the air, over all of it.

00:16:35.674 --> 00:16:35.949
You have to realize that you have that power and authority.

00:16:35.949 --> 00:16:38.879
If Jesus did it, we can do it.

00:16:38.879 --> 00:16:41.227
As he is, so are we in this world.

00:16:41.227 --> 00:16:42.062
That's what the Bible says.

00:16:52.479 --> 00:16:56.310
And I believe it.

00:16:56.310 --> 00:17:03.288
So you just need to know that because we're in storm season and they're already forecasting big storms tomorrow.

00:17:03.288 --> 00:17:07.030
I said, 'No, we ain't going to have no big storm tomorrow.

00:17:12.1000 --> 00:17:13.360
We're not going to have no high winds.

00:17:14.176 --> 00:17:16.759
We're not going to have major hail these things.

00:17:16.759 --> 00:17:28.217
' Over my area, over where I live, and where I put the tread of my soles, we're going to have peace over the weather.

00:17:28.217 --> 00:17:32.143
We're just going to have good rain.

00:17:32.143 --> 00:17:34.750
You just got to start saying that and believing it.

00:17:34.750 --> 00:17:40.159
You've got to believe it.

00:17:40.159 --> 00:17:46.986
You've got to put it in your heart and say it out of your mouth: 'I have authority over the storms.

00:17:51.970 --> 00:17:52.335
I have authority over the rain.

00:17:59.987 --> 00:18:00.320
I have authority over the clouds.

00:18:13.253 --> 00:18:13.387
I have authority over the sun.

00:18:13.387 --> 00:18:14.187
' I pray over it.

00:18:14.187 --> 00:18:20.453
If Joshua could delay the sun and do what he did and cause it to stand still.

00:18:24.840 --> 00:18:25.350
He was in the Old Covenant.

00:18:25.350 --> 00:18:30.440
Could God do that again for us if we needed it?

00:18:30.440 --> 00:18:41.519
I'm not saying we can just make the sun stand still all the time, but if we needed it, could God do it again?

00:18:41.519 --> 00:18:42.256
Yes.

00:18:42.256 --> 00:18:44.954
We're talking about the sun standing still.

00:18:44.954 --> 00:18:48.730
How much more could we call for some clouds?

00:18:59.060 --> 00:18:59.400
I see the cloud the size of a man's hand.

00:18:59.400 --> 00:19:13.120
If Elijah could cause the rain not to fall for three years because he prayed earnestly and interceded on behalf of the drought—telling it to be a drought and no rain to come—how much more could we do it?

00:19:13.120 --> 00:19:18.333
I don't want drought, but I'm calling for rain to come.

00:19:19.280 --> 00:19:20.120
That's what I'm talking about.

00:19:20.120 --> 00:19:20.983
We need rain.

00:19:20.983 --> 00:19:28.000
We need our lakes to be full, our ponds to be full, and our grass to be green.

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:29.872
Throughout the summer, we call for cooler temperatures.

00:19:29.872 --> 00:19:35.264
We aren't going to roast in 120 degrees; we're going to have cooler temperatures.

00:19:45.900 --> 00:19:46.190
I call cold fronts in from Canada, in the name of Jesus.

00:19:46.190 --> 00:19:50.273
Share some of that cold air, Canada.

00:19:50.273 --> 00:19:54.503
We call the cold air down in Jesus' name.

00:19:54.503 --> 00:20:00.824
That's what I tell them all summer: 'Share the air.

00:20:00.824 --> 00:20:06.620
You've got to share some of that air down here in the South; it's hot.

00:20:06.620 --> 00:20:09.620
' We've got to have some colder air down here.

